\c 11
\s Dambudziko regumi: Rufu rwamatangwe
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jehovha akati kuna Mosesi, "Ndichauyisa dambudziko rimwezve pamusoro paFarao napamusoro peIjipiti, ipapo achakutenderai kubva pano; musi waachakutenderai kuenda, zvirokwazvo achakudzingai chose pano.
\v 2 Zvino udza vanhu vanzwe, kuti murume mumwe nomumwe akumbire kunowokwake, nomukadzi mumwe nomumwe akumbire kunowokwake, vapiwe zvishongo zvesirivha nezvishongo zvendarama."
\v 3 Zvino Jehovha akapa vanhu nyasha pamberi pavaIjipiti. Naiye munhu uyu Mosesi, akanga ari mukuru kwazvo munyika yeIjipiti, pamberi pavaranda vaFarao, napamberi pavanhu.
\p
\v 4 Zvino Mosesi akati, "Zvanzi naJehovha, `Kana pava pakati pousiku, ndichabuda ndikafamba napakati peijipiti;
\v 5 madangwe ose munyika yeIjipiti achafa, kutanga padangwe raFarao anogara pachigaro choushe, kusvikira padangwe romurandakadzi ari paguyo, navana vose vemhongora dzezvipfuwo.
\v 6 Panyika yose yeijipiti pachava nokuchema kukuru, kwakadaro hakuna kumbovapo, uye hakungazovipozve.'
\v 7 Asi pakati pavana valsiraeri vose, pakati pavanhu kana zvipfuwo, hapangavi nembwa ichasimudza rurimi rwayo; kuti muzive kuti Jehovha akatsaura pakati pavaIjipiti navalsiraeri.
\v 8 Navaranda venyu vose ava vachaburukira kwandiri, vachandipfugamira, vachiti, Ibvai henyu, navanhu vose vanokuteverai; shure kwaizvozvo ndichabuda.' " Akabuda pamberi, paFarao, akatsamwa kwazvo.
\p
\v 9 Jehovha akati kuna Mosesi, "Farao haangakuteerereyi kuti zvishamiso zvangu zviwanzwe panyika yeIjipiti."
\v 10 Mosesisesi naAroni vakaita zvishamiso zviya zvose pamberi paFarao, asi Jehovha akaomesa mwoyo waFarao, akasatendera vana vaIsiraeri kubva munyika yake.
